#storecoin-roadmap.hc-feature.over-rel.lite.padding
  .hc-chunk.hc-customize-text-wrapper
    div.header
      h3.hc-feature-title Storecoin
        img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/storecoin-logo.png")
      p.hc-feature-lead 
        b +8-YEAR ROADMAP
      p.caption.footer-text *subject to change
      
    div.roadmap-years
      img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/roadmap-years-v2.png")
    
    div.row  
      div.roadmap-lists
        div.list
          div.head
            b Storecoin Launch
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/ico-rocket.png")
          ul
            li High-throughput consensus, up to 5,000+ transactions per second
            li Up to 220 validators; 22 launches the protocol
            li It is permissionless to perform work for the protocol but KYC/AML data is required for all types of decentralized workers; this enables future global KYC/AML compliance
            li
              img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/storecoin-logo.png", style="margin-left:0px;")
              | achieves censorship resistance because of the growing number of decentralized workers securing the protocol; rewards for workers grow as the number of workers grows; rewards are paid through new token inflation capped at 6%
            li The Storecoin Ecosystem Fund launches
            li Key patents are secured to protect against malicious hard forks outside of Governance
            li A secure engineering and CI/CD process is built to protect private keys from theft by any and all project contributors
            
        div.list
          div.head
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/storecoin-logo.png", style="margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0.3em;")
            b Wallet Released
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/ico-key.png")
          ul
            li Wallet distributes private keys
            li Private keys distributed to owners 
        
        div.column-head FEE-LESS, P2P PAYMENTS

      div.roadmap-lists
        div.list
          div.head
            b Storecoin Growth
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/ico-chart-up.png")
          ul
            li Up to 20,000 validator node participation
            li 50,000+ transactions per second
            li Once a threshold of 220 validators are reached, Decentralized Security Guard nodes (dGuards) are added to find bad actors throughout the protocol
            li Masternodes/eAgents are introduced for better throughput once +300 Validators are reached (Level 2 scaling)
            li A U.S. Constitution-inspired governance with checks and balances launches before 5/27/2021
            li Communication and Voting for Governance is hosted by decentralized Govnode workers making
              img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/storecoin-logo.png")
              |  Governance censorship resistant
            li U.S. Money Transmitter Licenses achieved
            li 
              img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/storecoin-logo.png", style="margin-left:0px;")
              |  moved to a non-profit foundation
            
        div.list
          div.head
            b Developer API
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/ico-api.png")
          ul
            li Wallet APIs for a programmable p2p currency
            li Built for mobile and web app developers
            li 
              img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/storecoin-logo.png", style="margin-left:0px;")
              |  Wallet is like Stripe but for storecoins
        
        div.column-head 
          b PLATFORM
          
      div.roadmap-lists
        div.list
          div.head
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/storecoin-logo.png", style="margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0.3em;")
            b APIs Mature
          ul
            li Stripe-like Wallet APIs enable third party app developers to build on top of the Storecoin blockchain using STORE tokens in their apps
            li The Storecoin Ecosystem Fund accelerates adoption of Wallet
            li Developers stake tokens to use Wallet; this helps prevent DDOS attacks
            
        div.list
          div.head
            b In-App Incentives
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/ico-wallet.png")
          ul
            li Powers in-app, incentivized API calls with
              img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/storecoin-logo.png")
