            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/ico-blockchain.png")
          ul
            li 250,000+ transactions per second
            
        div.list
          div.head
            b Global Consensus
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/ico-globe.png")
          ul
            li 222,000+ Validator nodes
        
        div.column-head 
          b CRYPTO-POWERED APPS 
          span(style="font-style: italic;")  (cApps)
            
      div.roadmap-lists
        div.list
          div.head
            b Smart Contracts
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/ico-contract.png")
          ul
            li Native protocol support for smart contracts
            li Smart contract client libraries in different languages
            li Smart contracts create a second design space
            li Developers stake tokens to build dApps on
              img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/storecoin-logo.png")
            
        div.list
          div.head
            b Chargebacks Supported
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/ico-cash-reg.png")
          ul
             li 
              img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/storecoin-logo.png", style="margin-left:0px;")
              |  being prepared for acceptance in cash registers around the world
             li Retailers would stake tokens to insure for chargebacks and more
             li Smart contracts enable a new decentralized worker called the sAgent to reach consensus on global Chargeback cases where
              img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/storecoin-logo.png")
              |  is used
              
        div.list
          div.head
            b Global KYC/AML Compliance
            img(src='/images/empty.png', data-src="/images/ico-law.png")
          ul
            li KYC and AML checks are compliant with the laws and national security demands of 190+ countries; this logic is hard coded into all decentralized worker nodes
            li If the laws of country X prevent transactions from being processed by decentralized nodes in country Y, the Storecoin protocol will support this natively, on chain
            li A long-term, security-first approach to building globally compliant infrastructure for zero-fee, p2p payments will give Storecoin developers the best opportunity to be embedded into banking and financial infrastructure around the globe.
        
        div.column-head 
